All Implemented Interfaces:
IAsciiCommand, IAsciiCommandResponder, IAsciiResponse
@Deprecated public class WriteAutorunFileCommand extends AsciiSelfResponderCommandBase
Deprecated.
Use AutorunCommand instead A command to write commands to the device's autorun file This command does not use the library marker and command index because they would be interpreted as part of the command to be added to the autorun file. So, by default, this command will capture non-library responses to allow synchronous commands to execute correctly.
